{"session_id": "a8d96970-0e9c-4be2-a62f-8d6e1cbe1495", "task": "Implement the following plan:\n\n# Cee \u2014 \u591a\u8a9e\u8a00 (zh-Hant / en) \u5be6\u4f5c\u8a08\u756b\n\n## Context\n\nCee \u76ee\u524d\u6240\u6709 UI \u5b57\u4e32\u5168\u90e8\u786c\u7de8\u78bc\u70ba\u82f1\u6587\uff0c\u7121\u4efb\u4f55 localization \u57fa\u790e\u8a2d\u65bd\u3002\n\u76ee\u6a19\uff1a\u52a0\u5165\u7e41\u9ad4\u4e2d\u6587 (zh-Hant) \u652f\u63f4\uff0c\u82f1\u6587\u70ba development language\u3002\n\n## \u6d89\u53ca\u6a94\u6848\n\n- `project.yml`\n- `Cee/App/AppDelegate.swift`\n- `Cee/Controllers/ImageViewController.swift`\n- `Cee/Views/EmptyStateView.swift`\n- `Cee/Views/ErrorPlaceholderView.swift`\n- `Cee/Views/StatusBarView.swift`\n- `Cee/en.lproj/Localizable.strings` (\u65b0\u5efa)\n- `Cee/zh-Hant.lproj/Localizable.strings` (\u65b0\u5efa)\n\n---\n\n## Step 1 \u2014 project.yml\n\n\u5728 `settings.base` \u52a0\u5165\uff1a\n\n```yaml\nsettings:\n  base:\n    SWIFT_VERSION: \"6\"\n    ARCHS: arm64\n    MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET: \"14.0\"\n    DEVELOPMENT_LANGUAGE: en          # \u2190 \u65b0\u589e\n```\n\nXcodeGen \u6703\u81ea\u52d5\u6383\u5165 `Cee/en.lproj/` \u548c `Cee/zh-Hant.lproj/` \u4e0b\u7684 `.strings` \u6a94\u3002\n\n---\n\n## Step 2 \u2014 \u5efa\u7acb Localizable.strings\n\n### Key \u547d\u540d\u898f\u5247\n\u5e73\u5766 dot-notation\uff0c\u4f9d\u9078\u55ae/\u529f\u80fd\u5206\u7d44\uff1a\n`menu.app.*`, `menu.file.*`, `menu.view.*`, `menu.navigation.*`, `menu.go.*`, `menu.window.*`\n`empty.*`, `error.*`, `status.*`\n\n### `Cee/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n\n```strings\n/* App Menu */\n\"menu.app.about\" = \"About Cee\";\n\"menu.app.quit\" = \"Quit Cee\";\n\n/* File Menu */\n\"menu.file.title\" = \"File\";\n\"menu.file.open\" = \"Open\\u2026\";\n\"menu.file.copyImage\" = \"Copy Image\";\n\"menu.file.revealInFinder\" = \"Reveal in Finder\";\n\"menu.file.closeWindow\" = \"Close Window\";\n\n/* View Menu */\n\"menu.view.title\" = \"View\";\n\"menu.view.fitOnScreen\" = \"Fit on Screen\";\n\"menu.view.actualSize\" = \"Actual Size\";\n\"menu.view.zoomIn\" = \"Zoom In\";\n\"menu.view.zoomOut\" = \"Zoom Out\";\n\"menu.view.alwaysFit\" = \"Always Fit Opened Images\";\n\"menu.view.fittingOptions\" = \"Fitting Options\";\n\"menu.view.shrinkH\" = \"Shrink to Fit Horizontally\";\n\"menu.view.shrinkV\" = \"Shrink to Fit Vertically\";\n\"menu.view.stretchH\" = \"Stretch to Fit Horizontally\";\n\"menu.view.stretchV\" = \"Stretch to Fit Vertically\";\n\"menu.view.scalingQuality\" = \"Scaling Quality\";\n\"menu.view.scalingLow\" = \"Low\";\n\"menu.view.scalingMedium\" = \"Medium\";\n\"menu.view.scalingHigh\" = \"High\";\n\"menu.view.showPixels\" = \"Show Pixels When Zooming I", "stage": "apply", "user_decision": "approve", "edit_distance": 0.09205020920502094, "user_feedback_text": "", "change_type": "config", "turn_number": 3, "_swechat_pushback": "non_pushback", "_swechat_persona": "expert_nitpicker", "_swechat_mode": "vibe", "_swechat_intent": "create new code", "_swechat_success": "82.0", "_swechat_agent_pct": 90.7949790794979}
